snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin': Graffiti Groovin' - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Y'all already know what time it is.

GRAFFITI GROOVIN IS NOW AVAILABLE ON GAMEBANANA:
https://gamebanana.com/mods/409366

As I'm writing this, Graffiti Groovin V2 has been confirmed and is currently on development, I'll make sure to post the trailer as soon as it's ready to be released.
